    "patch_code": "public boolean apply(Node n) {\n  // when the node is null it means we reached the Implicit return where the function returns(possibly without an return statement)\n  if (n == null) {\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  // when the node is call to function that pass one of the dep variable to non-side effect function\n  if (n.isCall() && !NodeUtil.functionCall has side effect(n)) {\n    return true;\n  }\n  // when the node is new call to function that pass one of the dep variable to non-side effect function\n  if (n.isNew() && !NodeUtil.constructorCall has side effect(n)) {\n    return true;\n  }\n\n  for (Node c = n.getFirst child(); c != null; c = c.getNext()) {\n    if (!control flow graph.is entering new cfgt node(c) && apply(c)) {\n      return true;\n    }\n  }\n  return false;\n}",
